Needed to change /boot/config.txt to add in dtoverlay=spi1-3cs - this enables the second channel of SPI.
From stack exchange below.

https://raspberrypi.stackexchange.com/questions/61430/i-want-to-use-spi0-and-spi1-at-the-same-time

Also installed https://github.com/mrwunderbar666/Python-RPi-MCP4922 for the DAC Control and the Adafruit MCP3008 library.
https://learn.adafruit.com/raspberry-pi-analog-to-digital-converters?view=all

Installed matplotlib via

sudo apt-get install python3-matplotlib



